FNF Another Friday Night - Chrome Extension
Dive into the rhythm with FNF Another Friday Night, the exciting Chrome Extension that takes your musical battles to a whole new level!

Challenge a variety of opponents in intense rap battles where your timing and rhythm skills are put to the test.
